      "text": "A person may have difficulty remembering a sequence of steps, or they",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "text": " ",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "text": "may find an overly complex user interface difficult to process and manage.",
      "type": "text"
    }
